UsersController
#index - HOME page today's carts with links to edit, Add New Cart button
#show - PROFILE page with username, email[, reset password link]

PrefabStoreController - nested resource of Users
  #index - show all the prefab stores for the user - name, link to edit, link to delete
  #edit (doubles as #show) - lets you update the name, add tags, remove tags
  #new - lets you make a new one: define a name + define, add, and remove tags
  #delete - confirm that user is ok with all cart_stores that use this prefab_store losing the prefab_store's tags

PrefabItemsController - nested resource of Users
#index - show all the user's prefab items, name, link to edit, link to delete
#edit (doubles as #show) - lets you update the name, add tags, remove tags
#new - lets you make a new one: give a name and add tags
#delete - confirm that user is ok with all cart_items that use this prefab_item losing the prefab_item's tags

TagController - nested resource of Users
#index - show all tags: name, link to details, link to delete
#new - give name, select prefab items and prefab stores to add the tag to
#edit (doubles as #show) - name, all the user's prefab items and stores that use it
#delete - confirm that user is ok with all prefabs, cart stores, and cart items losing this tag

CartsController - nested resource of Users
#index - show all the user's carts, with links to edit and delete
#edit (doubles as #show) - lets you change date, note. lets you edit and delete the items. lets you add new items. let you edit store.
#new - form to make a new cart.
  date, note

  store_prefab dropdown
  store note field for cart_store
  store tags field for cart_store - bunch of checkboxes?

  3 cart_item forms, for each:
  - price (required)
  - note (optional)
  - dropdown to select a prefab item (optional)
  - checkboxes for item tags (optional)


Order:
Tags,
Prefab Stores,
Prefab Items,
Carts,
User,
Navbar

Navbar:
New Cart -> Carts#new
Carts -> Carts#index
Stores -> PrefabStores#index
Items -> PrefabItems#index
DONE Tags -> Tags#index
DONE Signout -> Sessions#Logout
DONE Home -> Users#index
Profile -> Users#show
